 {
  "date": "2016-04-09 18:58", 
  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772527/", 
  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t一、祈使句的分类</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t祈使句表请求、命令、叮嘱、邀请、劝告等.祈使句分为第二人称祈使句及第&mdash;、三人称祈使句两大类.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t1．第二人称祈使句通常用来向听话者发出命令,提出要求或建议.这种祈使句的主语you通常不表示出来,而是以动词原形开头.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Stand up!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Don&rsquo;t worry about!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t但如果说话时有多人在场,就得把主语表示出来,或加呼语,以便指明是向谁提出请求或发出命令.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Parents with children go the front!带孩子的家长到前面去!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mary clean the windows,and you boys wash the floor!玛丽擦窗户,你们男孩子洗地板!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Come in,everybody!每个人都进来!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t有时将主语表示出来是为了加强语气或表示&ldquo;不高兴&rdquo;、&ldquo;厌烦&rdquo;、&ldquo;鄙视&rdquo;等情绪.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Don&rsquo;t you be late again!你可别再迟到了!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;You get out of here!你给我滚出去!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mind your own business,you!你少管闲事!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t2．第一、三人称祈使句是以第一人称和第三人称代词或者名词等作为祈使的对象,这类祈使句通常以let为引导词表建议.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Let&rsquo;s go!Let us go home!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Let him be here by 10 o&rsquo;clock．</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t祈使句除用谓语动词表示外,还可用名词、副词、动词短语等表示.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Help!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Patience!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Quickly!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Hands up!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t二、祈使句的强调形式及否定形式</div>\n<div style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">祈使句的强调形式是在整个结构之前加do.如：</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Do be careful!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Do Stop talking!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Do give my regards to your parents!务必／一定代我向你父母问好!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t祈使句的否定形式是在整个结构之前加don&rsquo;t或never.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Don&rsquo;t you be nervous!你不要紧张!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t以let为引导词的祈使句的否定形式通常是在Let&rsquo;s或Let us／me后加not.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Let&rsquo;s not waste our time arguing about it!咱们别浪费时间争论这事了!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Let&rsquo;s not say anything about it!这事咱们谁也别说!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t但英式英语也用这样的表达：Don&rsquo;t let&rsquo;s say anything about it.</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772527/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772527\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772429/\">剩女有错吗？SK-II广告在朋友圈刷出新高度</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772157/\">我们男神都有“绅士手”！绅士手英文怎么说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772398/\">刷爆Instagram的父女插画 爸比是我的守护神</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771876/\">致有梦想的你：如何成为生活的赢家？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772422/\">被英语的双关坑大了！明明按照指示做 结果……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772092/\">抖森以Loki身份客串天气预报：天都萌哭了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771949/\">除了疯狂动物城 还有哪些动物好片值得一看</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772416/\">英语六级作文常用8大句型（一）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772215/\">纪录片《我们女王90岁》：凯特王妃领衔爆料</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771232/\">6个暖心小故事 旅行中邂逅的美好爱情(2)</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_b